<h2>Learning Journey</h2>
<p>Planning for next 6 months</p>
<p>Quick links:<a href="/sdl.pdf">Draft--Self Directed Learning</a></p>
<ul>
<li>Goals:</li>
</ul>
<p>1.Understand 'learning and Education' in depth.</p>
<p>2.Personal Growth.</p>
<p>3.Search for future workspace/area.</p>
<ul>
<li>How:</li>
</ul>
<p>Understand 'Learning and Education' under the guidance of mentors.</p>
<p>Do different experiments for personal growth.</p>
<p>Search for future working space during this journey.</p>
<p>1.1 Mentors:</p>
<p>Community of people who have:</p>
<p>Written books on education, children and learning;Devoted their lives to the world of children;Successfully started alternate schools around the world;Introduced ‘unschooling’ of archaic methods;Promoted homeschooling;Written blogs and articles on educating children on the web;Shared TED talks and other Youtube videos;Met us and shared their journey.</p><p>Children themselves are biggest mentors for us.</p>
<p>1.2 Curriculum:</p>
<p>It is learning journey so curriculum will be in informal way. Education is like an ocean.So first we will make one broad mind map including all learning types, and other aspects of Education. After that we will choose subject areas and select books to read, place to observe, people to meet for understanding that subject area. Apart from that we will study educational psychology, philosophy and methods.</p>
<p>2.1 Personal Growth:</p>
<p>Do self exploration. Know more about ourselves.</p>
<p>Learn to live sustainable.</p>
<p>Learn about human rights, environment sustainability and sustainable development.</p>
<p>Do different creative projects with 'Swapathgami' community.</p>
<p>1.3 Search for future workspace:</p>
<p>We will meet different people and organizations during this journey. It will help to find or make new path for future.</p>
